%% ReOrg AI — User Flows

%% Flow 1: Onboarding
graph TD
    A[Landing Page] --> B[Register]
    B --> C[Create Tenant]
    C --> D[Invite Team Members]
    D --> E[Dashboard]

%% Flow 2: Project Creation
graph TD
    A2[Dashboard] --> B2[Select Tenant]
    B2 --> C2[Create Project]
    C2 --> D2[Configure Project]
    D2 --> E2[Project Overview]

%% Flow 3: Data Intake
graph TD
    A3[Project Overview] --> B3[Upload Documents]
    B3 --> C3[Preview & PII Check]
    C3 -->|PII Detected| D3[Sanitize]
    D3 --> C3
    C3 -->|Clean| E3[Map Columns]
    E3 --> F3[Validate]
    F3 --> G3[Confirm & Load]

%% Flow 4: Phase Execution
graph TD
    A4[Phase Workspace] --> B4[Check Prerequisites]
    B4 -->|Met| C4[Run Phase]
    B4 -->|Not Met| D4[Show Blockers]
    C4 --> E4[Monitor Progress]
    E4 --> F4[Review Results]
    F4 --> G4[Gate Checklist]
    G4 -->|Pass| H4[Unlock Next Phase]
    G4 -->|Fail| I4[Back to Fix]

%% Flow 5: Output Generation
graph TD
    A5[Outputs Tab] --> B5[Select Artifacts]
    B5 --> C5[Build Report]
    C5 --> D5[Preview Report]
    D5 --> E5[Export Bundle]
